snippet.title: Amber Heard Was Arrested For Domestic Violence
snippet.description:
Amber Heard was arrested for domestic violence against her former girlfriend, it has been claimed.
The actress, who has been granted a temporary restraining order against her husband Johnny Depp, was allegedly arrested after an incident involving her ex Tasya Van Ree in 2009. 
According to sources, the actress and Van Ree got into an argument in 2009, whereby Amber was said to have "grabbed Van Ree's arm" and was arrested and detained for misdemeanor domestic violence. 
Reports said that her mug shot was taken and that she appeared in court the following day. However, a prosecutor declined to move forward with the case.
